\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 COMMERCIAL CAPITAL}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I\u8217\'92ve called you all for a task of great importance. You all know I\u8217\'92m tracking the murder of Prince Ygne.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Leto: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Death. Death of Prince Ygne. Unless you have news to share with us, Zima?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Security footage at the scene and a tip from a crime ring in Outer Rim. Foreman mentioned \u8216\'91The Illuminati\u8217\'92.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93There\u8217\'92s a woman with a green ring we\u8217\'92re looking for, and whatever group she\u8217\'92s part of is bound to be here.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Leto: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93\u8230\'85That\u8217\'92s all you have to go on?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: (There\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s a moment of silence. This isn\u8217\'92t going to be easy.)}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Vesna: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Hey, where the hell is Veter?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Osen: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Drunk in a ditch somewhere, no doubt!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Padat: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93She should not be missing this meeting.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Leto: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Fill her in later! It\u8217\'92s her own damn fault.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Leto: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93*If* we want to find this \u8216\'91Illuminati\u8217\'92, Zima\u8230\'85\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Leto: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93We would have to pay visits to each of the Dons.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Vesna: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93There\u8217\'92s three Dons in Commercial. Each one has a huge amount of money and influence over this town.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Osen: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93They pretty much own the place.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Vesna: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93If this goes all the way to the top like you think it does, the Dons will know about it. But it wouldn\u8217\'92t be easy. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Padat: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93We would be walking into hotspots of crime.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Padat: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93And how do we know that your hunch will be worth this risk?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: (And I hate to involve a group of irate Justs, but here we are.)}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You\u8217\'92re not wrong. I\u8217\'92ll do this on my own if I have to.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 *If the player has been killing a lot*}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Leto: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Hang on. Let\u8217\'92s talk about your fighting, Zima. We\u8217\'92ve heard you\u8217\'92ve been doing a lot of it.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Osen: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Yeah, like a lot! And killing too!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Leto: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Maybe taking things too far for a servant of the people.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Padat: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You will not make many friends with this kind of approach.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: (Vesna moves out from against the wall.)}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Vesna: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I don\u8217\'92t think it\u8217\'92s so bad. Zima\u8217\'92s just doing her job right? Scaring all the widdle baddies straight?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Leto: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Yeah, that kind of crazy says you know how to handle yourself.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Leto: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93But\u8230\'85 play it a bit cooler from now on, ok Just?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93\u8230\'85\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Mh, I\u8217\'92ll keep it in mind.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Then with your minds ever so at ease, will you join me?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \}}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 *If the player has been arresting a lot*}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Leto: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Normally, I wouldn\u8217\'92t join you. This hunch could put all our lives in danger. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Leto: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93But you\u8217\'92ve earned a reputation among Justs.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Vesna: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I think you could be a little tougher on people. Just my preference.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Osen: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93No, you\u8217\'92ve been doing a good job!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Padat: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93It is not always easy to spare someone in the heat of battle, yet you do.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Thanks everyone. Then, will you join me?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \}}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: (Vesna nods.)}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Vesna: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I\u8217\'92ll take any chance to make some noise in Commercial.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: (Osen and Padat step forward.)}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Padat: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93The Commercial Capital is large and loosely governed. We are the best help you will get.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Osen: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93We can show you around and help you meet the Dons! It\u8217\'92ll be fun!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: (Leto puts her fist in.)}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Leto: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93We\u8217\'92re Justs right? We gotta stick together.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Then we\u8217\'92re a team. Let\u8217\'92s pay a visit to these Dons.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Vesna: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93We\u8217\'92ll split up for recon and wait on you to start moving.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Leto: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Find Veter for us, would you?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Leto: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93She\u8217\'92s probably off drinking somewhere.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: (One by one they take their leave. I let out a breath of air.)}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I\u8217\'92m hoping this hunch is right too.\u8221\'94}
