\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Royal citizens, the Kingdom has concluded that the blast that claimed the life of Prince Ygne was caused by a bomb planted on the car.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93This act of terrorism is believed to be an attack from a foreign nation.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93In response, the Kingdom has raised tariffs on imported goods including food and entertainment items, and raised security at borders.\u8221\'94}
